Detection Limits and Other Information On CCAL's Analytes

limits.Rd

Metadata including the detection limits for various analytes that are measured by CCAL and used by IMD.

Usage

limits

Format

limits

A data frame with 15 rows and 11 columns:

analysis

The description of the analyte as found in the "Analysis" column at https://ccal.oregonstate.edu/detection.

analyte_code

The abbreviation for the analyte used by CCAL in their deliverables.
